    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on Indian citizens",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Some Indian nationals working in Sri Lanka have been attacked in the Naula area.",
        "Naula Police said that an attack was made on some Indian nationals who were swimming in Powatenna Reservoir of Naula-Meekolla area and a suspect was arrested.",
        "Initial investigations revealed that the reason for the incident was a conflict of opinion between the two parties.",
        "It has also been revealed that the said Indian nationals are working in development projects being carried out by the government in Naula area."
      ],
